   [spacer.gif]
   CDC SLATED FOR BILLIONS IN ADDITIONAL FUNDS FOR BIO-TERRORISM
   PREPAREDNESS
   [spacer.gif]
   Senator Max Cleland (D-GA) today announced the final passage of the
   Labor-HHS Appropriations Conference Report and the Department of
   Defense Appropriations Conference Report. Together the two bills
   provide billions in funding for the Centers for Disease Control and
   Prevention in Atlanta.
   [spacer.gif]
   CLELAND ANNOUNCES SENATE CONFIRMATION OF ASHLEY ROYAL FOR MIDDLE
   DISTRICT JUDICIAL POST
   [spacer.gif]
   U.S. Senator Max Cleland (D-GA) today announced the Senate confirmation
   of Ashley Royal to be a federal judge for the U.S. District Court in
   the Middle District of Georgia. Royal has worked in private practice,
   taught at the University of Georgia School of Law and the University
   College of Mercer University.
   [spacer.gif]
